[normal]LPG 03[bold]&#xa0;[bold]Written submission from Hampshire County Council (LPG 03)[bold]This submission is in three parts:[bold]Part I[bold]              [bold]Executive Summary[bold]Part II[bold]              [bold]Response to questions 1 to 6[bold]Part III[bold]              [bold]Recommended areas for further review and analysis[bold]&#xa0;[bold]Part I[bold]Executive Summary[bold]&#xa0;
